# Remotion PMM Video Conventions

## Structure

- Keep compositions in `remotion-pmm/src/` with a clear, readable scene layout.
- Store JSON briefs in `remotion-pmm/briefs/`.
- Render outputs go to `remotion-pmm/out/`.

## Coding guidelines

- Keep scene durations explicit and readable.
- Prefer data‑driven rendering from JSON props.
- Ensure typography and colors are consistent with brand.
- Keep the copy concise and outcome‑focused.

## Quality checks

- Each scene has a clear narrative purpose.
- Evidence is shown on screen when possible.
- CTA is explicit and aligned to persona.
